  icon: {fileID: 0}
  speechSound: {fileID: 0}
  timePerLetter: 0.05
  startDialogue:
  - "We\u2019ll have\u2026 - the\u2026 - *!!!"
  - "Ey, you. Gimme a *. - Don\u2019t worry about One, he\u2019s just cranky because
    of the cone. - Cone? Ice cream cone?! WHERE?!"
  - "Give us a * and prepare for trouble! - Make it\u2026 triple? This doesn\u2019t
    work. - WOOF! That\u2019s right!"
  - "Ey, you. Gimme a *. - Don\u2019t worry about One, he\u2019s just cranky because
    of the cone. - Cone? Ice cream cone?! WHERE?!"
  - A * is all we can afford because of Two and her incessant spending. - Hey, we
    needed those bracelets! - I love bracelets!
  repeatDialogue:
  - "What you lookin\u2019 at, punk? - I bet they\u2019re looking at my beautiful
